  "texts": [
    "Achieving more precise simulations of energy consumption is crucial for gaining a better understanding of energy management in electric transport and ultimately contributing to a sustainable future with enhanced convenience in terms of distance range and recharging time.",
    "This paper addresses the problem of energy consumption simulation for EVs using various software packages and offers insights on making the simulation process more precise.",
    "By doing so, engineers can develop improved energy management strategies for EVs.",
    "Computer simulation plays a crucial role in the development and optimization of EV systems, and accurate modeling is a central challenge.",
    "Specific testing cycles such as NEDC, JC-08, and EPA cycle are utilized for powertrain simulation and optimization in different regions."
  ],
